1
00:00:01,631 --> 00:00:05,840
On Self Realization and Sahaja Yoga
自觉与霎哈嘉瑜伽

2
00:00:06,234 --> 00:00:11,514
as soon as you start any work in any place, first of all they want Me to cure people
当你在任何地方开始任何工作 首先 他们想让你治疗人们

3
00:00:12,014 --> 00:00:14,014
and to help them with curatives
用各种疗法来帮助他们

4
00:00:14,691 --> 00:00:21,163
Now if I pay attention more to that, then the main work is to create doctors out of everyone
现在如果我放更多的注意力在那些事上 那么主要的工作就是让人们都成为医生

5
00:00:21,486 --> 00:00:26,840
That is neglected. Then you become unpopular. They think, “Oh, She is not sympathetic” and this and that
不是那样的 然后你变得不受欢迎 他们想 噢 祂没有同情心 这个那个

6
00:00:27,269 --> 00:00:31,420
But now as we have everybody can cure now everyone, I don’t cure anyone directly
但现在由于我们每个人都能治疗别人 我不用直接治疗任何人

7
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:38,133
But they don’t like it. They want I should be there and then you to be pampered and all those things are there, rather difficult
但他们不喜欢那样 他们想让我在那里 满足他们的自我 所有的那些事 相当困难

8
00:00:38,633 --> 00:00:41,173
It’s not that we are not running an election, you see
我们并不是在竞选

9
00:00:41,354 --> 00:00:45,646
like we should please others, sort of this is not there. whatever is the reality
好像我们应该取悦人 不是这样 我们的事都是真实的

10
00:00:46,465 --> 00:00:50,942
if a person has intelligence – pure intelligence 
如果一个人有智力 纯粹的智力

11
00:00:51,442 --> 00:00:54,105
he can see that this is something very different
他会看到 这是非常不同的事

12
00:00:54,605 --> 00:00:59,229
and for that one has to understand that you cannot
为此 我们必须明白你不能

13
00:00:59,913 --> 00:01:06,721
you cannot force on anyone that you get your realization
你不能强迫任何人得到自觉

14
00:01:06,749 --> 00:01:10,630
In the same way you cannot force Me that I give you realization
同样地 你也不能强迫我给予你自觉

15
00:01:10,933 --> 00:01:13,949
because if it does not work it does not work. It’s such a living force you see
因为如果它不起作用它就不会起作用 它是一个活生生的力量 你看

16
00:01:14,685 --> 00:01:16,812
 and that upsets them very soon.
而且那很快会使他们心烦意乱

17
00:01:17,758 --> 00:01:24,334
I feel that the way this industrial revolution has come in the west
我感到 在西方这场工业革命到来的方式

18
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:29,337
people have lost their moorings. Perhaps they are so confused
使人们不知在何处停泊 也许他们如此迷惑

19
00:01:29,837 --> 00:01:33,633
With all these gurus coming down here confusing them
所有这些导师来到这里令他们迷惑

20
00:01:34,028 --> 00:01:37,140
and all kinds of new things coming, they don’t know where to look.
各种新事物来到 他们不知该看向哪里

21
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:41,520
But unless and until you get your evolution completed
但除非你的进化得以完成

22
00:01:41,692 --> 00:01:45,201
unless and until you reach that absolute state of understanding
除非你达到绝对理解的状态

23
00:01:45,478 --> 00:01:46,680
the chaos will remain
否则混乱仍将继续

24
00:01:47,138 --> 00:01:49,497
So one has to try to get to that
因此 一个人必须尽力达到那

25
00:01:50,141 --> 00:01:52,379
But one must understand you can’t pay for it
但必须明白你不能为此而付费

26
00:01:52,722 --> 00:01:53,910
There is no effort
无需费力
